~ what_do_mean
Cecil: Well, you had to do something to get sent down here. So, you're either a terrible person or you made a deal.
- I don't belong here.
	=> i_dont_belong_here
- I don't think I did either of those.
	=> neither_of_those

~ dont_remember_dying
Cecil: Huh, it could be possession then. I heard that humans who experience prolonged possession often forget what they did when they were possessed or how they died for awhile after getting here. You'll remember eventually. 
