~ floor_404_info
Cecil: Don't you know anything? When you're caught acting up or not performing well enough, they send you to reconditioning on Floor 404. They act like it's some kind of vacation or retreat, but it's the WORST thing that can happen to you.
- What happens there?
	=> what_happens_there

~ what_happens_there
Cecil: Well I- I... I don't know exactly! I just know that when demons get sent there, they come back wrong. Disturbed! Whatever it is they do down there, we should all do our best to not learn what it is.
- Right, thanks. I'll be going now.
	=> END